- pom.xml also sets maven.compiler.source/target to 1.7 and many .java source files exist under src/main/java, confirming Java as the language.
- The project contains a start-class property (io.github.proxyprint.kitchen.WebAppConfig) and a WebAppConfig.java under src/main/java, plus many controllers and models (packages controllers, models), which matches a Spring MVC application structure.
- Build system: Maven (pom.xml).
